00:24:20,260 --> 00:24:21,500
Stay away from Ji Chengchuan.

439
00:24:21,700 --> 00:24:22,300
He's mine.

440
00:24:28,500 --> 00:24:29,020
Song Yao.

441
00:24:29,660 --> 00:24:30,500
There are things

