458
00:26:26,220 --> 00:26:26,780
Bye-bye.

459
00:26:37,500 --> 00:26:38,300
Qiao!

460
00:26:38,300 --> 00:26:39,020
We love you!

461
00:26:39,180 --> 00:26:40,940
