00:27:18,740 --> 00:27:19,220
This is...

468
00:27:30,260 --> 00:27:31,060
My gosh.

469
00:27:31,860 --> 00:27:32,500
What do you think?

470
00:27:33,460 --> 00:27:34,260
You like it?

471
00:27:42,860 --> 00:27:45,180
