482
00:28:06,580 --> 00:28:07,140
Understand?

483
00:28:09,540 --> 00:28:10,100
No.

484
00:28:10,220 --> 00:28:10,860
Not at all.

485
00:28:11,420 --> 00:28:12,780
I'm wasting my time
explaining to you two.

486
00:28:13,460 --> 00:28:13,900
