507
00:28:59,700 --> 00:29:00,700
You knew?

508
00:29:00,820 --> 00:29:01,540
Of course.

509
00:29:02,300 --> 00:29:03,780
Song Yao and I are on the same side.

510
00:29:06,980 --> 00:29:07,580
Regarding this matter,

511
00:29:07,980 --> 00:29:09,540
