526
00:29:33,980 --> 00:29:35,180
You two just have to assist me.

527
00:29:35,500 --> 00:29:36,260
Understand?

528
00:29:39,100 --> 00:29:39,820
Yes... stand.

529
00:29:40,020 --> 00:29:40,630
Okay.

